當免檢疫証明係生意咁做，搵班阿姐派傳單幫人攪。<br />\n每日中港司機都幾千人出出入入。<br />\n<br />\n4.煲大件事！比全世界多D人知道，只有多D人覺醒，知道個政府係棄全香港巿民安危不顧，先會爭取到更多人企係我哋呢邊，同我哋一齊抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟姊妹各自爬山 他日平安相聚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1c9166cfbfe23011373f1f00e8467431e482cf","tid":2106544,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:24:01.000Z","msg":"無知一問，依d 書店大路既書有冇得賣？例如 衛斯理，同1984。想買一整套衛斯理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c083417961f5e8bc549280fbc561a00d07e1a0","tid":2106544,"uid":183649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c1c9166cfbfe23011373f1f00e8467431e482cf","tid":2106544,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:24:01.000Z","msg":"無知一問，依d 書店大路既書有冇得賣？例如 衛斯理，同1984。想買一整套衛斯理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:26:41.000Z","msg":"1984 周圍都有<br />\n衛斯理全套就有難度，等其他巴絲指教"},{"pid":"8457d79c10b386de1660bc5742352f6aa9c2df7c","tid":2106544,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4cd1531181b264bc894f81afbbbc9ca5e071d32","tid":2106544,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"旺角幾間樓上都會去"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:34:18.000Z","msg":"我搵唔到邊度上去序言<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482268bc673830c8b0ad75ea1b29a4f83751b98d","tid":2106544,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8457d79c10b386de1660bc5742352f6aa9c2df7c","tid":2106544,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4cd1531181b264bc894f81afbbbc9ca5e071d32","tid":2106544,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"旺角幾間樓上都