ink?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F717725661678807%2Fposts%2F3017860118332005%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=673a6bd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/717725661678807/posts/3017860118332005/</a><br />\n親愛的朋友，<br />\n<br />\n因第三波疫情爆發，香港書展2020延期了。<br />\n<br />\n我們都曾經掙扎，因已經付出了不少費用(搭建費，運輸費，貨款&hellip;😭😭) 損失慘重，但欣喜可以保障員工及顧客的安全。<br />\n<br />\n書展將改為在書店/網上舉行，詳情稍後公佈。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝各位支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>呢度有良心書店list</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=124125275849334&amp;id=102587704669758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D124125275849334%26id%3D102587704669758&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=7b7ccc1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=124125275849334&amp;id=102587704669758</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重要既係<br />\n拒絕三中商！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"除了愉林，仲有好多黃書店要幫手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbWFzg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbWFzg3.jpg&h=20a0875f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:20:14.000Z","msg":"聯合咁多書店整個網上購物日 / 香港人書店爆買日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268b0c9b5b404dfd16a65ab6ec10fa77d67b7c6c","tid":2106544,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c2c7d57d3e56e7ef9b42512296d96785f319d1be","tid":2106544,"uid":176447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4c1c9166cfbfe23011373f1f00e8467431e482cf","tid":2106544,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:24:01.000Z","msg":"無知一問，依d 書店大路既書有冇得賣？例如 衛斯理，同1984。想買一整套衛斯理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:25:11.000Z","msg":"大路書去愉林 田園 樂文 多啲 港島去森記<br />\n唔得可以搵書店訂 衛斯理咁大路唔難的"},{"pid":"039f7ae6f9c5bbff12fa7a05c01108627e878590","tid":2106544,"uid":135040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4cd1531181b264bc894f81afbbbc9ca5e071d32","tid":2106544,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"旺角幾間樓上都會去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"西洋菜街一次就係哂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028f88897f4bcd46b5f77f0bb0cead4db6df8030","tid":2106544,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bff0853833f0ff7e58672db247df368f1c44a9fc","tid":2106544,"uid":20916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8457d79c10b386de1660bc5742352f6aa9c2df7c","tid":2106544,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4cd1531181b264bc894f81afbbbc9ca5e071d32","tid":2106544,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"旺角幾間樓上都會去"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:34:18.000Z","msg":"我搵唔到邊度上去序言<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"旺角E2出口，經過bodyshop過馬路，沿住條街搵68號大廈上7樓就係，幾步架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"唔該晒教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去親旺角多數都係去田園<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efe5cac2d4df307e0065655dc0af59ecb787f99","tid":2106544,"uid":95452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61ff5d663db78806b73a77b7152c565ff4c878ad","tid":2106544,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:48:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E6%A6%86%E6%9E%97%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25A6%2586%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25BA%2597%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=f1f189a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E6%A6%86%E6%9E%97%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n榆林書店事件<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n榆林書店事件，源於同志團體香港彩虹不滿榆林書局拒絕擺放同性戀者心路歷程小冊子《她們的女性印記》，指書店以宗教理由封殺「性傾向平等資訊」。<br />\n<br />\n背景<br />\n<br />\n2005年，同志團體「香港彩虹」制作了小冊子《她們的女性印記》，希望把小冊子於榆林書店擺放，榆林書店方面亦答應要求，但事後有人發現有關小冊子《她們的女性印記》，全部被丟棄於書店後的垃圾桶，因而引起有關組織之不滿，並發起抗議行動。<br />\n<br />\n爭論<br />\n<br />\n事件於很多時事論壇及基版中都有很大的爭論，一方面有人認為榆林書店是私人機構，書店有權選擇擺放甚麼書。另一方面有人認為書店方面並沒有表明其反對同性戀立場，並大方地准許有關小冊子擺放，事後卻不動聲色地把所有小冊子丟到垃圾桶，行為十分卑劣。<br />\n<br />\n回響<br />\n<br />\n事件後許多人才知道榆林書店原來是有基督教背景，並以基督教信仰作為經營理念，有關書店似有歧視同性戀之嫌，於是引起抵制有關書店之呼籲。此外亦引起書店是否屬公共空間、何謂公共領域等討論。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"咁基督教本身係唔比同性戀嘛"}]}